About our House Company.

Marketing and Advertising

  • our company is responsible for preparing lease agreements and rental contracts that outline the terms and conditions of the rental arrangement. They ensure legal compliance and protect the interests of both property owners and tenants.
  • Rent Collection and Financial Management: our management companies collect rent on behalf of property owners and ensure timely payment. They may also manage security deposits, handle financial records, and provide owners with regular financial statements.
  • Property Maintenance and Repairs: Property management companies oversee the maintenance and repair needs of rental properties. They coordinate routine maintenance, address tenant-reported issues, and ensure that properties are in good condition.
